msgstr "and get familiar with how it feels,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:31.3"
msgid "Khīyati nopacīyati,"
msgstr "you wear away, you don’t heap up:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:31.4"
msgid "evaṃ so caratī sato;"
msgstr "that’s how to live mindfully."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:31.5"
msgid "Evaṃ apacinato dukkhaṃ,"
msgstr "Eroding suffering like this,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:31.6"
msgid "santike nibbāna vuccati."
msgstr "you’re said to be in the presence of extinguishment."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc32"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.95:32.1"
msgid "Na so rajjati phassesu,"
msgstr "When you sense a touch with mindfulness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:32.2"
msgid "phassaṃ phussa paṭissato;"
msgstr "there’s no desire for touches."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:32.3"
msgid "Virattacitto vedeti,"
msgstr "Experiencing it with a mind free of desire,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:32.4"
msgid "tañca nājjhosa tiṭṭhati."
msgstr "you don’t keep clinging to it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc33"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.95:33.1"
msgid "Yathāssa phusato phassaṃ,"
msgstr "Even as you sense a touch"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:33.2"
msgid "sevato cāpi vedanaṃ;"
msgstr "and get familiar with how it feels,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:33.3"
msgid "Khīyati nopacīyati,"
msgstr "you wear away, you don’t heap up:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:33.4"
msgid "evaṃ so caratī sato;"
msgstr "that’s how to live mindfully."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:33.5"
msgid "Evaṃ apacinato dukkhaṃ,"
msgstr "Eroding suffering like this,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:33.6"
msgid "santike nibbāna vuccati."
msgstr "you’re said to be in the presence of extinguishment."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.76"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc34"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.95:34.1"
msgid "Na so rajjati dhammesu,"
msgstr "When you know a thought with mindfulness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:34.2"
msgid "dhammaṃ ñatvā paṭissato;"
msgstr "there’s no desire for thoughts."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:34.3"
msgid "Virattacitto vedeti,"
msgstr "Experiencing it with a mind free of desire,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:34.4"
msgid "tañca nājjhosa tiṭṭhati."
msgstr "you don’t keep clinging to it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc35"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.95:35.1"
msgid "Yathāssa jānato dhammaṃ,"
msgstr "Even as you know a thought"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:35.2"
msgid "Sevato cāpi vedanaṃ;"
msgstr "and get familiar with how it feels,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:35.3"
msgid "Khīyati nopacīyati,"
msgstr "you wear away, you don’t heap up:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:35.4"
msgid "Evaṃ so caratī sato;"
msgstr "that’s how to live mindfully."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:35.5"
msgid "Evaṃ apacinato dukkhaṃ,"
msgstr "Eroding suffering like this,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:35.6"
msgid "Santike nibbāna vuccatī’ti."
msgstr "you’re said to be in the presence of extinguishment.’"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc36"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.95:36.1"
msgid "Imassa khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmī”ti."
msgstr "That’s how I understand the detailed meaning of the Buddha’s brief statement.”"

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn35.95:36.2"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, mālukyaputta."
msgstr "“Good, good, Māluṅkyaputta!"

msgctxt "sn35.95:36.3"
msgid "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, mālukyaputta, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsi:"
msgstr "It’s good that you understand the detailed meaning of what I’ve said in brief like this."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc37"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.95:37.1"
msgid "‘Rūpaṃ disvā sati muṭṭhā,"
msgstr "(The Buddha repeats the verses in full.)"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:37.2"
msgid "Piyaṃ nimittaṃ manasi karoto;"
msgstr "as attention latches on a pleasant feature."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:37.3"
msgid "Sārattacitto vedeti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:37.4"
msgid "Tañca ajjhosa tiṭṭhati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc38"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.1"
msgid "Tassa vaḍḍhanti vedanā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.2"
msgid "anekā rūpasambhavā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.3"
msgid "Abhijjhā ca vihesā ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.4"
msgid "cittamassūpahaññati;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.5"
msgid "Evaṃ ācinato dukkhaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.6"
msgid "ārā nibbāna vuccati."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.7"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
